搜尋










文史哲的英文怎麼說
                    中文拼音 [wénshǐ]
                    




文史哲英文
                    journal of literature history and philosophy
文: Ⅰ名詞1 （字） character; script; writing 2 （文字） language 3 （文章） literary composition; wri...史: 名詞1 （歷史） history 2 （古代掌管記載史事的官） an official who was in charge of historical rec...史哲: albert schweitzer 
																※中文詞彙文史哲在字典百科國語字典中的解釋。
										





 


例句







                                    Staid men and good scholars at first expressed mirth and then indignation at the audacity that baptised this gay rag bag english literature, then philosophy of history, then human culture.                                    



                                    持重的人和淵博的學者起初看了覺得好笑，繼而勃然大怒，說我居然敢把那些破布爛絮--美其名曰英國文學、歷史哲學、人類文化。                                    




                                    The history research of institute of literature history and philosophy shandong university, mainly includes two main attack directions, the research of the chinese history theory and the research of the the qin and han dynasty history, holds the some space in this discipline domain, has deeply academic accumulates, many discovered has had widespread and the lasting influence, recognized as the academic circles                                    



文史哲研究院的史學研究，主要包括中國史學理論研究和秦漢史研究兩個主攻方向，均在本學科領域佔有一席之地，具有深厚的學術積澱，許多創獲已產生了廣泛而持久的影響，為學術界所公認。                                    




                                    Philosophy of science ; social philosophy ; ethics ; aesthetics ; confucianism ; chinese intellectual history ; and philosophy of literature ; and theory of the humanities                                    



                                    科學哲學社會哲學倫理學美學儒家思想中國思想史;文學哲學                                    




                                    A series of e - learning projects featuring culture, education, arts appreciation and language learning was launched to provide an interactive learning platform with multi - media content for net - users all over the world                                    



                                    推出網上學習e - learning ，透過網際網路多媒體互動平臺，推動終身學習，提供文史哲藝術欣賞和語言學習的素材，提高大眾學習興趣。                                    




                                    At research postgraduate level, lingnan offers mphil and phd programmes in chinese, cultural studies, english, history, philosophy, translation, visual studies, business including accounting, finance, insurance, international business, management, marketing, operation research and decision sciences, and social sciences including economics, politics and sociology                                    



                                    招生的學位課程包括中文文化研究英文歷史哲學翻譯視覺藝術商學包括會計財務保險國際企業管理市場學運籌學及決策科學及社會科學包括：經濟政治及社會學。獲錄取的研究生將就特定範疇進行深入研究工作。                                    









 




